main event: An observer in York, Pennsylvania reported seeing a bright, stationary object hovering over the treetops that moved in deliberate directions and had illuminated characteristics.
interesting points: The object was observed for about 25 minutes.
The object was positioned in the west and was described as almost stationary.
The observer considered the object to be illuminated.
The report states the object had characteristics that alleged it was illuminated.
No photographs were provided with the report.
sighted object: a bright, stationary object with illuminated characteristics
